    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/237">Heinricus</persName> divina favente clementia
                        Romanorum imperator augustus. Si sanctarum aecclesiarum ordines corroborare
                        studuerimus, intercessores illos apud Deum pro nostris facinoribus esse non
                        dubitamus. Idcirco noverit omnium fidelium sanctae Dei aecclesiae,
                        nostrrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum industria, qualiter <persName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Abbots" ref="#people/2125"
                            >Benedictus</persName> venerabilis abbas <orgName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Monasteries #Churches #Cells/hermitages #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fisheries #Saltworks #Sea_salt #Fruits/vegetables #Wine #Cereals #Legumes #Oil #Mountains #Hay/fodder #Animals #Mills #Slave_labour #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Immunity"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/130"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                            Sancti Salvatoris, quod dicitur Sextus</orgName>, in <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/210"><rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/4"
                            >Luccensi</placeName></geogName> situm pietatem nostram adiit, et ut
                        bona aecclesiae suae per nostri <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">praecepti
                            paginam</rs>, secundum <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Exceptive"
                            >antecessom nostrorum concessionem</rs> ibi confirmaremus suppliciter
                        postulavit. Cuius iustae petitioni aures nostrae pietatis adhibens, ob
                        interventum <persName key="#marriage" ref="#people/365">Agnetis</persName>
                        nostri imperii nostrique thori carissimae <rs key="#marriage"
                        >consortis</rs>, ac petitione <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/2130"
                            >Opizonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarii</rs> nostri, idem monasterium cum <rs
                            key="#Churches">aecclesiis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">capellis</rs> seu <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curtibus</rs> cunctisque <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> tam
                        quas modo habet quamque etiam in futuro Deo adiuvante iuste et legaliter
                        acquirere poterit, tam infra <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> Luccam quam et
                        de foris. Quarum aecclesiarum vocabula sunt: aecclesiae Sanctorum <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2034">Benedicti</orgName> et
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2035"
                            >Anastasii</orgName>, <orgName key="#Churches">aecclesia domini
                            Salvatoris que dicitur Astrude</orgName>, <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2017">aecclesia sancti Ambrosii in <placeName
                                key="#Churches" ref="#places/633">Ascleto</placeName></orgName>,
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2016">aecclesia sancti
                            Pauli</orgName> in <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2442"
                            >Coselle</placeName>, <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2023">sancti Antonii</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Churches">aecclesia sancti Philippi</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2024">aecclesia sancti
                            Petri</orgName>, <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2025"
                            >Columbani</orgName>, <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2027">aecclesia sancti Augustini</orgName>,
                            <orgName key="#Churches">aecclesia sancti Martini</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Churches">aecclesia sancti Andreae in Monte</orgName> cum omni sua
                        pertinentia, et medietas <orgName key="#Churches">aecclesiae sanctae
                            Mariae</orgName> et <orgName key="#Churches">sancti Petri</orgName> cum
                        universis pertinentiis suis, quas venerabilis <persName ref="#people/2126"
                            key="#Commutatio #Abbots">Maius</persName> abbas mutuavit cum <persName
                            key="#Commutatio #Marquis/duke" ref="#people/3">Hugone</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchione</rs> sibi in vicem ad proprietatem, et
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2018">aecclesia domini
                            Salvatoris</orgName> quae dicitur <placeName ref="#places/755"
                            key="#Churches">Controne</placeName> et <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2009">curtem quae dicitur <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                >Cervaria</placeName></geogName>, et <geogName ref="#estates/2008"
                            key="#Curtes">curtem quae dicitur <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2420">Quarphinem</placeName></geogName>, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">praedia</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/597">Castellione</placeName> et
                        de <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/2428"
                            >Camisana</placeName> et <placeName key="#Landed_possessions"
                            ref="#places/2427">in loco qui dicitur Valli</placeName> et in
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/202"
                            >Carricini</placeName>, et in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/2421">Verrucola</placeName>;
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2009">aecclesia sancti Petri</orgName>
                        in <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2422">Gragno</placeName>,
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2010">aecclesia sancti
                            Prosperi</orgName> in <placeName ref="#places/283" key="#Churches"
                            >Blentina</placeName>, <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2086">aecclesia sancti Donini</orgName> in
                            <placeName key="#Castle #Churches" ref="#places/2443"
                            >Vuingule</placeName> cum <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs>. Simul et
                        aliis aecclesiis: <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2019" key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesia</orgName> quae est infra castellum de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2424" key="#Castle #Churches">Cerritulo</placeName>, cum
                        medietate ipsius castelli, <orgName>aecclesia</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#places/2426">Palagia</placeName> cum suis
                        pertinentiis, <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2020">aecclesia sancti
                            Angeli</orgName> in <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2429"
                            >Nebula</placeName>, <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2029">curtem
                            de <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/239"
                            >Quarrazana</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2029">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2444">Filcini</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2011">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2430">Cosiniano</placeName></geogName>, et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2033"><placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2445">Brisciniana</placeName></geogName>; <orgName
                            key="#Churches">aecclesia sancti Martini</orgName> in <placeName
                            key="#Churches">Ferignano</placeName>, et in <placeName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#places/2447">Vinziana</placeName>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2090">aecclesia sancti
                            Petri</orgName> et in <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2448"
                            >Leugnano</placeName>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">aecclesia sancti Petri</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2089">sancti Gregorii</orgName>,
                        et in <geogName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches"
                            ref="#estates/2012"><placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/319"
                                >Capiano</placeName> curtem</geogName> cum aecclesiis, id est
                        aecclesia <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2091">sancti Quirici</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2092">sancti Miniati</orgName>,
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2093">sancti
                            Salvatoris</orgName>, <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2094">sancti Savini</orgName>, <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2095">sancti Pauli</orgName>,
                        cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis, aquarumque
                            decursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscariis</rs>, venationibus, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>. <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2010"
                            >Curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/2425"
                                >Camiliano</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2028">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2449">Casanova</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes">curtem de Vallis</geogName> cum aecclesia suisque
                        pertinentiis et quicquid dinoscitur habere in <geogName ref="#estates/79"
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/66"
                                >Pisano</placeName></geogName>: hoc est <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2035">curtem <placeName ref="#places/2455" key="#Curtes"
                                >sancti Cristofori</placeName></geogName>, et in <placeName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#places/2457">Tabiano</placeName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2013">aecclesiam sancti Benedicti</orgName>
                        quae est in <placeName ref="#places/2450" key="#Churches"
                            >Septimo</placeName> cum suis pertinentiis et quicquid iudicavit et
                        destinavit eidem monasterio <persName>Uualfredus</persName> filius
                            <persName>Bonifacii</persName> de iam dicto castello et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes">curtem de Septimo</geogName>, et quandam nostri iuris
                        terram sitam iuxta civitatem Pisam prope terram filiorum
                            <persName>Chuniberti</persName> quae est in mensura sistariorum VII. Et
                            <geogName ref="#estates/2013" key="#Curtes">curtem sancti Petri in
                                <placeName ref="#places/284">Petritulo</placeName></geogName>,
                            <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2014">curtem sancti Fridiani in
                                <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/2431"
                            >Tredeci</placeName></geogName>, curtes tres in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Churches" ref="#places/1004">Centoria</placeName> cum
                        aecclesia <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2011" key="#Churches">sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2096">Sancti Georgi</orgName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes">curtem de Angelo</geogName> et medietatem aecclesiae
                            <orgName key="#Churches">sancti Angeli</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Churches">Armizana</placeName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            >curtem de Rainano</geogName>, collem de <placeName ref="#places/2452"
                            >Malandrone</placeName>, aecclesia <orgName key="#Churches">sancti
                            Comici</orgName> iuxta <orgName>fluvium Cicina</orgName>, et <rs
                            key="#Saltworks #Sea_salt">salinae</rs> quae sunt in <placeName
                            key="#Saltworks #Sea_salt" ref="#places/2451">Campo Maiore</placeName>
                        prope <placeName key="#Saltworks #Sea_salt" ref="#places/556"
                            >Cicina</placeName>, <geogName>curtem de Fontana</geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2015">curtem de Valle Blancana</geogName>,
                        prope <placeName ref="#places/2432">Bibonem</placeName>, et quod habet in
                            <geogName ref="#estates/86" key="#Comitatus">comitatu <placeName
                                key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/91">Cornino</placeName></geogName>:
                        hoc est <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2016">curtem de <placeName
                                key="#Curtes">Massa</placeName></geogName> et <orgName>aecclesia
                            sancti Genesii</orgName> cum sua pertinentia et <orgName>aecclesia
                            sancti Petri</orgName> in <placeName>Publico</placeName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2017">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2433">Bibiano</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2018">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2434">Lano</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2019">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2435">Rofena</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2020">curtem de Sarmena</geogName> cum
                            <orgName>aecclesia sancti Obtabiani</orgName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2021">curtem de
                            <placeName>Caspuniano</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2022">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2437">Agnano</placeName></geogName>, cum
                            <orgName>aecclesia sanctae Mariae</orgName>, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2023">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2438">Urceatico</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2024">curtem de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2439">Leguli</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2025"
                            ><placeName>Meletuli</placeName></geogName>, et ali quantas partes de
                        terra ubi quondamn fuit aecclesia sancti Iusti, <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2026">curtem in <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/2440">Vingale</placeName></geogName> in <placeName
                            key="#Mansi">Carpuniano</placeName> unum <rs key="#Mansi">mansum</rs>,
                        in <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/2441">Pino</placeName> III <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Domuscultae #Hay/fodder">mansos</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Domuscultae">dominicalibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs> et medietatem castelli in <placeName
                            key="#Castle">Campo Marci</placeName>. In <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/185">comitatu <placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/507">Pistoriensi</placeName></geogName> aecclesiam
                        sancti Abundi cum campo Ieronimi. In <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/154">comitatu <placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/273">Rosellense</placeName></geogName> necnon et in
                            <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/161"><placeName
                                key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/53">Parmense</placeName></geogName> et
                        infra <rs key="#Islands">insulam</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Islands">Corsicam</placeName> quicquid habet una cum
                        curtibus, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">hortis</rs>, terris, <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals #Legumes">campis</rs>, mansis, tam
                        dominicalibus a quam et massariciis, aldiaritiis, tributariis, <rs
                            key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>, silvis, <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>,
                        alpibus, <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pasquis</rs>, paludibus, areis
                        piscariis, salinariis, <rs key="#Mills">molendinus</rs>, aquis aquarumque
                        ductibus, <rs key="#Slave_labour">servis et ancillis</rs>, <rs key="#Aldius"
                            >aldiis et aldiabus</rs> utriusque sexus, et cum omnibus quae dici vel
                        nominari possunt ad predictum monasterium Sancti Salvatoris in Sexto
                        pertinentibus vel aspicientibus nostra regia potestate prout iuste et
                        legaliter possumus confirmamus, modisque omnibus corroboramus. Liceat quidem
                        eidem coenobio de propria congregatione abbatem eligere, si regulariter
                        vixerint et duos <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >advocatos</rs> habere. His autem adiungimus <rs key="#Conductores">XII
                            liberos homines</rs>, cum quibus rem prelibati coenobii acquirant et
                        defendant. Quibus ut nullum tortum maliadiciatur transfundimus ac delegamus,
                        sed potestatem habeant fruendi, ordinandi, commutandi vel quicquid utilitas
                        aecclesiae seu fratrum fuerit inde faciendi. Precipientes itaque <rs
                            key="#Immunity">iubemus ut nullus dux, marchio, episcopus comes,
                            vicecomes, scoldachius, gastaldio, nullaque nostri imperii magna seu
                            parva persona predictum monasterium de omnibus predictis rebus iniuste
                            inquietare, molestare, disvestire, vel potestative in eo hospicium
                            facere aut ad aliquam publicam functionem cogere sine legali presumat
                            iudicio</rs>. Qui vero hoc fecerit sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras mille</rs>, medietatem <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">camerae nostrae</rs>, et medietatem predicto
                        monasterio. Quod ut verius credatur firmiterque ab omnibus observetur,
                        inpressione sigilli nostri, ut inferius videtur, iussimus insigniri. Signum
                        domini Heinrici tercii regis invictissimi. (M.) secundi Romanorum
                        imperatoris augusti. SMP. <persName key="#Chancellor" ref="#people/2130"
                            >Opizo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> vice <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Archbishops" ref="#people/2129"
                            >Herimanni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> et <rs key="#Archbishops"
                            >archiepiscopi</rs> recognovi. Data II Id. iulii. Anno dominicae
                        incarnationis Millesimo LIII, indictione VI. Anno autem domni Heinrici
                        tercii regis imperatoris secundi ordinationis eius XXV, regni XV, Imperii
                        VII. Actum <placeName ref="#places/2419">Mindon</placeName>, in Dei nomine
                        feliciter. Amen. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
